01:47:32.740 --> 01:47:34.032
[Bu Indah] Diam!

1401
01:47:35.073 --> 01:47:35.907
Hidup Laras!

1402
01:47:36.865 --> 01:47:37.698
[Bu Indah] Diam!

1403
01:47:40.365 --> 01:47:41.240
Laras!

1404
01:47:51.073 --> 01:47:54.448
Dengan hormat, kami meminta kamu

1405
01:47:55.115 --> 01:47:58.448
untuk tidak melanjutkan
tahun terakhir kamu di SMA Cahaya.


1406
01:47:59.157 --> 01:48:00.157
Baik, Bu.

1407
01:48:00.990 --> 01:48:03.990
[suara sorak-sorai murid]

1408
01:48:37.615 --> 01:48:38.782
Keren!

