01:48:44.448 --> 01:48:45.448
<i>"Dear David,</i>

1410
01:48:46.323 --> 01:48:47.865
gue sayang sama lu.

1411
01:48:47.948 --> 01:48:50.198
Dari sang Penulis, Laras."

1412
01:48:52.407 --> 01:48:55.073
Gue cuma mau bilang kalau gue juga…

1413
01:49:02.073 --> 01:49:05.032
[lagu "King and Lionheart" mengalun]

1414
01:49:17.740 --> 01:49:18.698
- Hai.
- Hai.


1415
01:49:22.115 --> 01:49:24.532
Bagaimana rasanya berenang
sama ikan-ikan ini?


1416
01:49:26.073 --> 01:49:28.365
Rasanya kayak

1417
01:49:29.240 --> 01:49:31.157
terbang bareng ikan-ikan.

1418
01:49:32.282 --> 01:49:33.448
- Terbang?
- <i>He-em.</i>


1419
01:49:33.532 --> 01:49:34.657
Gue Anya.

1420
01:49:37.032 --> 01:49:38.198
Dilla.

1421
01:49:43.490 --> 01:49:44.448
Bapak David?

1422
01:49:56.407 --> 01:49:57.448
[Cece] Fendi, Fendi…

1423
01:49:58.323 --> 01:50:00.282
[Dilla] Tan, udah baca <i>Dear David,</i> belum?

